name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: We could not have been happier with the service and support from Kasandra and the team at Lexmerca. They took the stress out of having bought a new home, always keeping us informed and managing the process seamlessly. The team were experienced and professional, but also incredibly friendly and willing to answer all of our ‘new home buyer’ questions along the way. Would highly recommend to anyone!

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: Rhianne is professional and very reliable. We are very lucky to have her helping us throughout the contract review and settlement process. We are in good hands, very grateful to have her guiding us during the process.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: Jason and Kayla are amazing. They are considerate and very professional in all their services. We have used them for residential and commercial property and importantly, they have provided advice and council that has placed us in a position of financial safety. We would not use any other solicitors other than Lexmerca.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: Horrible lawyers. Highly incompetent in my opinion. Bungled involvement with the matter I was involved in. Go elsewhere!
owner_answer: Chloe, we have no record of representing you or providing you with any services. If Chloe Peters is your real name, you are not a client of ours. If you are using an alias, we encourage you to contact John or Jason at Lexmerca to discuss your concerns.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: As first home buyers who were somewhat unfamiliar with the process, Lexmerca were amazing! A big thank you to Jason and Kasandra - you were professional, friendly and made the purchase of our home smooth, seamless and easy to understand.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: Jacinta Geaghan came highly recommended to us when seeking conveyancing for buying a property, and we can’t recommend her highly enough ourselves now. She was so friendly, explained details to us clearly and always responded quickly and in full. Thank you!

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: The Lexmerca team are outstanding and their attention to detail was second to none. They provided tailored solutions for our conveyancing needs with constant communication and follow up. Very responsive to all requests. Nothing was too difficult for the team. I would not hesitate to recommend Firmin and Kasandra to anybody buying or selling a home.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: If there was a zero option, that’s exactly what I would put. This firm provided the worst service and treated clients terribly. One, they place an inexperienced lawyer to handle our case which resulted in losing our Stamp duty concession (they ended up paying). Two the Manager, in writing called a client of the firm a liar, once proven wrong there was no apology. Three, was provided a reasonable price of fees at the start then charged extra at the end. Instead of having an exciting experience being first home owners it left us extremely stressed and unhappy. I will never use this firm ever again. Don’t waste your time or money.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: Really appreciate Jacinta's help in assisting purchasing a property. The whole process was smooth and well-scheduled! Thank you!

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text:
I worked with Firman Kwong. There were a number of issues and I was extremely anxious and stressed. However, Firman was very reassuring, made me feel calm and he worked above and beyond to make sure that we were successful

In the past I have worked with a number of contractual lawyers and Firman has been the best because of his relationships with the client.

Thank you Firman.

name: Lexmerca Lawyers
review_text: Without a doubt, the most useless bunch of ‘lawyers’ god put breath into. 🙄
